00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,400
Let me ask you,

300
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,640
would you take photos if you went there for fun?

301
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:40,800
Wouldn't that leave evidence against yourself?

302
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,800
Secretly filmed.

303
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,170
It must have been secretly filmed.

304
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:45,930
Go investigate.

305
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,280
It has nothing to do with me.

306
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:47,920
Liu Jiang,

307
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,930
you just said something

308
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,600
that makes a lot of sense.

309
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,620
Of all the people in the photo,

310
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,180
besides this girl,

311
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,600
you are the only one still alive.

312
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,080
So,

313
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,440
do you think your current situation

314
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:02,640
is dangerous?

315
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,530
Listen to me, Liu Jiang.

316
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,240
You already understand

317
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,570
the current situation.

318
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:13,880
The reason we're telling you so much

319
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,040
is to protect you.

320
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,920
But you

321
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,860
must also give us a reason to protect you.

322
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,460
Take another careful look this time.

323
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,280
I'm thirsty.

324
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,520
Oh.

325
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:32,920
Caicai.

326
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,680
Huh?

327
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:35,960
Hey.

328
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,220
This is for you,

329
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,840
a little purple princess.

330
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,000
Daddy doesn't know her name either,

331
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,240
but I think she looks

332
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,400
exactly like you.

333
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:42,960
Right?

334
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:44,970
Come here, let Daddy give you a hug.

335
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:47,280
Look at you,

336
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,240
buying dolls all day.

337
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,320
There's no room at home.

338
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,000
What a waste of money.

339
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,040
So what?

340
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:53,000
Money is meant to make Caicai happy.

341
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,000
As long as you like it,

342
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,880
Daddy will buy you a different doll every day.

343
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:56,840
Red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, purple.

344
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,720
I'll buy them all for you, okay?

345
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:58,160
Okay.

346
00:12:58,760 --> 00:12:59,200
Daddy,

347
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:01,760
I made this at kindergarten today.

348
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:02,720
Oh.

349
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,360
Is this...

350
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,360
Did you make this?

351
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:05,840
By yourself?

352
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:08,520
Aww.

353
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:11,280
Daddy loves it so much.

354
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:12,530
Give Daddy a hug.

355
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:13,360
Oh,

356
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:15,040
thank you, Caicai.

357
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:19,080
Caicai, listen to Daddy.

358
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,610
If one day Daddy isn't around anymore,

359
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:24,780
you have to listen to Mommy, okay?

360
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,340
Promise Daddy.

361
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,320
Okay.

362
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:28,640
Let's go.

363
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:29,840
Let's go home and eat.

364
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:30,840
Let's go.

365
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,320
Look.

366
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,040
It dropped.

367
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:32,520
Let's go.

368
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:32,840
Let's go.

369
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,840
Let's hold hands.

370
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:23,880
You wait here.

371
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,960
I'll go check it out.

372
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,360
Okay.

373
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:11,090
Who is it?

374
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:13,940
You shouldn't have

375
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:16,240
given my number to your wife.

376
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,360
What do you mean?

377
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,800
You asked me to meet you here.

378
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:24,880
It stinks in here.

379
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:25,560
With the crap you've done,

380
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,560
just stay inside.

381
00:15:26,800 --> 00:15:28,680
I thought about having my wife call you.

382
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:29,920
But the cops are watching me.

383
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:30,850
I'm telling you.

384
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:33,420
If I call you, the cops will investigate you.

385
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:36,440
Don't rush me.

386
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,700
I'm only halfway done.

387
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,240
You ruined it.

388
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:42,820
I haven't even finished using the bathroom.

389
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:44,360
I'll talk to you when I get out.

390
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:44,720
Hey!

391
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:48,290
What do you mean?

392
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:49,770
What do you mean?

393
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:50,920
Open it.

394
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,400
Open the door!

395
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:54,640
If you aren't afraid of the cops outside hearing,

396
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,500
keep knocking.

397
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:00,440
Let me ask you.

398
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,600
Who killed these people?

399
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:04,680
How should I know?

400
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:05,940
Could it be because

401
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,920
of what happened back then?

402
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:10,200
You were the one who handled it.

403
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,680
You said you handled it cleanly.

404
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:12,600
Absolutely clean.

405
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:14,460
I handled it absolutely cleanly.

406
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:16,000
What exactly is going on?

407
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,280
Bothering me every day.

408
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:19,200
Are you hiding something from me?

409
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:28,840
I think

410
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,120
right now,

411
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,360
it's quite dangerous.

412
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:32,280
I think we

413
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,400
should go lay low

414
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:36,160
to avoid the risk.

415
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,160
Back then,

416
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:39,640
you had the money to fund the cripple.

417
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:40,360
So could you

418
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:41,690
spare a little to fund me

419
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:42,960
now?

420
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:46,560
Let go of me.

421
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,600
The cripple dared to steal from me

422
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,200
and ask for money through you

423
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,520
because back then...

424
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,370
Someone testified for him.

425
00:16:56,880 --> 00:16:57,760
What about now?

426
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:00,840
Who else?

427
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,359
Oh.

428
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:07,730
You killed them.

429
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,079
Now you want to kill me.

430
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:11,660
If I wanted to kill you,

431
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,819
it wouldn't be this much trouble.

432
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,040
Oh my god.

433
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:22,319
Liu Jiang.

434
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,400
You have to remember,

435
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:28,359
you have a wife and kids.

436
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,200
Now,

437
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:32,120
we must keep our mouths shut.

438
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:34,560
Except for us,

439
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:38,280
no one else can bring that up.

440
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,980
Go hide out for a while.

441
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,160
After things cool down,

442
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,160
you can come back.

443
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:53,520
Don't go.

444
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:55,520
Don't go.
